txt.en: Wanted: Sinister wings from Azanulbizar to aid the Haban'akkâ of Thráin. Reward to be granted upon delivery.
As promised, you have received a modest reward for delivering the trophies sought by the Haban'akkâ of Thráin.
Haban'akkâ of Thráin Task: Sinister Wings
The Dwarves of the Haban'akkâ have posted a task to collect sinister wings at Azanulbizar. These can be turned in for a reward.
Deliver the sinister wings to a collection box
You have accepted a task to acquire sinister wings for the Haban'akkâ of Thráin.
Wanted: Sinister wings from Azanulbizar to aid the Haban'akkâ of Thráin.
